sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant NPM as npm scripts
    participant Vite as Vite dev server
    participant Br as Browser
    participant API as Backend API
    participant VT as Vitest
    participant QA as tsc and eslint
    participant Git as Git and CI

    Note over Dev,API: Start the stack once per session
    Dev->>NPM: npm run db:up
    Dev->>NPM: npm run backend
    Dev->>NPM: npm run frontend
    NPM->>Vite: start dev server (HMR and /api proxy)
    Vite-->>Br: serve app at 127.0.0.1:5173

    loop Inner loop: edit and see
        Dev->>Vite: edit .tsx / .ts / .scss in src/
        Vite-->>Br: hot module replacement, no full reload
        Br->>API: fetch /api/... through the proxy
        API-->>Br: JSON response
        Dev->>Br: check the result on screen
    end

    Note over Dev,VT: Prove it with tests
    Dev->>VT: add .test.tsx / .test.ts (RTL and jsdom, stub fetch)
    Dev->>NPM: npm run test:frontend
    NPM->>VT: vitest run
    VT-->>Dev: pass or fail

    Note over Dev,QA: Gate before commit
    Dev->>NPM: npm run typecheck
    Dev->>NPM: npm run lint:frontend
    Dev->>NPM: npm run build
    NPM->>QA: tsc -b, eslint, vite build
    QA-->>Dev: pass or fail

    Dev->>Git: commit, push, open PR
    Git->>Git: Checks workflow: setup, lint, build, test
    Git-->>Dev: green check or failure
